content:
Each CRM Analytics Growth and CRM Analytics Plus license is a single-user license that provides access to CRM Analytics. The license limits your instance of the CRM Analytics to 1 billion rows of data. If you require more data, you can purchase additional rows.

CRM Analytics license data storage limits are contractual, not technical. Licensee agrees to strictly monitor its total number of data rows.

The CRM Analytics Growth license includes two prebuilt permission sets: CRM Analytics Growth Admin and CRM Analytics Growth User. The CRM Analytics Plus license includes two prebuilt permission sets: CRM Analytics Plus Admin and CRM Analytics Plus User.

Basic setup involves choosing and assigning the prebuilt permission sets. Advanced setup allows you to create custom CRM Analytics permission sets. When assigning any CRM Analytics permission set, Salesforce auto-assigns the CRM Analytics Growth permission set license to that user.

You can assign a CRM Analytics permission set license along with other Salesforce user licenses.
